Chapter.Section:
Examples Section

 This worksheet exercises example and log commands in comment mode.

Tested examples


gap> comment_example_value := 2 + 3;
5




gap> comment_alias_example := 3 + 4;
7




gap> 10 - 3;
7




gap> 6 * 7;
42







Untested logs


gap> comment_log_value := 9;
9




gap> comment_alias_log := 11;
11




gap> "comment log session";
"comment log session"




gap> "comment alias log session";
"comment alias log session"
